{"tid":627877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★日本擬立法封鎖盜版動畫漫畫網站 打擊侵權行為","createTime":"2018-04-13T10:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:03:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa1fbfcc365398701ca09dd9b640b4d386a8ff2","tid":627877,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"日本政府計劃立法封鎖盜版動畫漫畫網站，打擊侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n首相安倍晉三出席有關知識產權幕僚會議，指盜版動漫網站對業界傷害急速擴大，必須及早訂立對策。<br />\n<br />\n會議決定，將以立法方式封鎖盜版動漫網站，即使設置網上連結到盜版網站，又或者令網民更容易由搜尋器找到盜版網站，都可能受罰。法案將於明年提交國會。<br />\n<br />\n不過網絡供應商質疑，方案變相要監管用戶的網上活動，侵犯通訊私隱，落實有困難。<br />\n<br />\n內容產業相關機構估計，過去半年，日本在版權方面損失超過四千億日圓，折合近三百億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5ad07e0fe60383f727d321fb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5ad07e0fe60383f727d321fb%2F&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGssP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=1696d8ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5ad07e0fe60383f727d321fb/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2d2c630b27005411ec4a3ff441ff5ce11b5372","tid":627877,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"how about AV?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e80b7e6c34310087fc892f993258d465de30e88","tid":627877,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"計唔計香港同大陸嗰啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68c2e2c6196c41e281500391dee5752ef71c401","tid":627877,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e80b7e6c34310087fc892f993258d465de30e88","tid":627877,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:56: